# Environment for testing the ci-image workflow locally with act.
#
# Usage:
#   cp .github/act/ci-image.env.example .github/act/ci-image.env
#   # Set GITHUB_TOKEN below, then:
#   make test-ci-ci-image
#
# The Makefile target passes dry_run=true and act sets ACT=true, so:
#   - The Docker build (TDLib compilation, ~15 min) is skipped entirely.
#   - No image is pushed to GHCR.
# The step is skipped at the workflow level when env.ACT == 'true'.
#
# GITHUB_TOKEN: needed for GHCR login step (skipped in act, but kept here for completeness).
# Generate at https://github.com/settings/tokens — required scope: write:packages
GITHUB_TOKEN=
